    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A Spiraling wall of black chakra appears to protect you. Until the start of your next turn, you gain a +3 bonus to AC and 8 DR (damage reduction) including against the triggering attack.</p><p>Also, you gain immunity to Psychic damage vs Genjutsu with the Visual, Auditory and/or Tactical keywords. This doesn't affect Genjutsu with Inhale.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and DR by +4.</p>",
